  <brief_title>Elimination of Protein-bound Uremic Retention Solutes by Prometheus Artificial Hepatic System Versus Conventional Dialysis</brief_title>
  <official_title>Elimination of Protein-bound Uremic Retention Solutes by Prometheus Artificial Hepatic System Versus Conventional Dialysis</official_title>
